<plot>The film Life Passion Death reveals the experience of a woman, Angela, full of dreams and passion for traveling and writing. Angela grows up in a small town in Spain where people remain all their lives in close emotional and physical proximity to their families. Only a few adventuresome souls like Angela are motivated to search for something beyond their comfortable small-town existence. Ultimately, Angela must choose between her passion or life in her home town near her family.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?335613</url></doc>
